{"tid":986633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發][無伏] 木村拓哉扮女裝","createTime":"2019-01-18T15:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T11:29:43.000Z","uid":16404,"like":36,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4ed5a72adf73643acca6406ce20feb276ebb7f5f","tid":986633,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:34:02.000Z","msg":"木村拓哉扮女裝嫵媚露臉　坐觀眾席無人發現<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20190118ent010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirrormedia.mg%2Fstory%2F20190118ent010&d=CGlvEuLvU3dvRpk9BeDIbwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=696dd8c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mirrormedia.mg/story/20190118ent010</a><br />\n<br />\n萬人迷木村拓哉的新片《假面酒店》即將在日本上映，他最近便頻頻亮相綜藝節目曝光力捧新片，昨晚（17日）他再亮相《人間觀察》，這次居然扮女人。<br />\n<br />\n節目中，木村更變身美貌的「女裝大佬」，扮工作人員招呼老牌演員笹野高史，木村多次斟茶遞咖啡，對方都認不出木村，直至笹野寫毛筆大字，木村上前幫忙，才近距離認出木村，當場笑個不停。<br />\n<br />\n其後木村現身錄影現場坐在觀眾席扮女粉絲，當日節目出席的嘉賓有小泉孝太郎、DAIGO、速水直道及一班諧星，但沒有一個人認出木村坐在觀眾席，直至木村上臺拿取笹野的墨寶，才認出女子正是木村假扮，全部人驚歎為之譁然。<br />\n<br />\n事後網友都大讚木村扮女人美豔又性感，絕對是美女，難怪能生出木村光希這樣的正妹女兒。<br />\n仔細一算，木村拓哉近期的出格宣傳，這次已經是第4波。第1波是木村拓哉扮收音師，演起工作人員，第2波是幫女粉絲洗頭，引起極大宣傳效果，第3波則是開導後輩，宣示大家都過著痛苦的生活，每一次的演出，效果都十分出色，可說是木村拓哉勇於突破自己的一系列挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/K3yLINx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK3yLINx.jpg&h=40ceece2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eCTR0Wm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeCTR0Wm.jpg&h=b8bfedd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/k1nqDZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fk1nqDZ1.jpg&h=44886212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Qr5taDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQr5taDm.jpg&h=ce6fe4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d8c7afa4b4037238c0487cb4b80ef15364a9b","tid":986633,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"又幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用錯icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19374ab287d6108015807383224d956c0bf26dbf","tid":986633,"uid":4597,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"好似蔡思貝"},{"pid":"6f3c0e8976ca05c8a0c2591dba2aa9e62bb6b56c","tid":986633,"uid":215823,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"好撚似蔡思達"},{"pid":"0c10d190bc667b217c9019f3f42f381aa401eb73","tid":986633,"uid":16404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"似咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e7215d70112a906083769daf603def7074c35b","tid":986633,"uid":52459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"木村思貝"},{"pid":"5bf48b4c911ad6068ffa8d561fb7baebe3822919","tid":986633,"uid":16404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22473b9d0d77ba81dedca2408dcb64040fd3509","tid":986633,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"第三張好似貝貝"},{"pid":"4b52d7530805a416eef50f8f61a4d02e8d960c36","tid":986633,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"木村光希黎"},{"pid":"d3e3d622223ac524d41dbb340adffa6b64a73206","tid":986633,"uid":27597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T02:22:49.000Z","msg":"蔡c達"},{"pid":"5c8c4fb27b4dfe91dd4e48a1f0910f525b22a56c","tid":986633,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:28:11.000Z","msg":"搞咩條友而家霉到要扮女人"},{"pid":"682a55e075